				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Gale speaks with his love interest player in a private bedroom upstairs at an inn. They've saved the world and just spent the night together. Now they take a moment to discuss what's in store for them. Gale will either:\r\n- Wish to retrieve a powerful (and dangerous) artefact that was lost during the climactic battle\r\n- Wish to return to his life in Waterdeep."
				}
